##ORAL RECORD | TRANS-PROVINCIAL TRANSPORTATION OF NUCLEIC ACID testing equipment

Micro-signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

You hear all the time about the nucleic acid test kit, where you can't tell if it's positive or negative, and you have to put it in the nucleic acid test equipment that I'm in charge of to get the results.

Dictation | Peng Xin
Arrangement | Huang Qi

Now everyone talks about going to Hubei, feel very scared. But because of work, I recently went to a few trips to Hubei, the second day of the New Year experience, it is particularly tortuous.
Peng Xin
I am an employee of Roche Diagnostics Customer Service Department, working in Changsha, Hunan Province. Generally speaking, my work is the after-sales training and service of the testing equipment. The product I'm in charge of is nucleic acid testing equipment. NUCLEIC ACID detection professional said is "viral nucleic acid load detection" , in the past may be many people do not understand these things, the new outbreak of pneumonia, the people across the country know "nucleic acid detection" .

You hear all the time about the nucleic acid test kit, where you can't tell if it's positive or negative, and you have to put it in the nucleic acid test equipment that I'm in charge of to get the results. Let's put it this way: The kit is the gas, our equipment is the car, the gas has to be added to the car, to run. My job is to teach people how to drive this car and maintain it.
Following the outbreak of pneumonia in COVID-19, Roche Diagnostics activated an emergency response mechanism from top to bottom, bringing together the company's efforts to ensure the accurate detection of our customers.
Equipment installed by Peng Xin
In order to increase nucleic acid detection, the recent epidemic-related units in Hubei need to install new nucleic acid detection equipment, we have a lot of tasks.

According to the usual procedure, we have special responsible for the installation of equipment colleagues, I have to wait for them to install after the training and debugging on the line. But in times of crisis, my mission has changed.
On the morning of the 2nd day of the Lunar New Year, I received a report from a colleague that the Jingmen Center for Disease Control and Prevention needed to install a LightCycler 480. At that time, the company had a stock of this instrument in Wuhan, but a colleague from Wuhan had to apply for a pass to travel to Wuhan, this pass must be returned to Wuhan on the same day. If he sends it there and installs it again, I'm afraid it will be too late. And Wuhan After-sales Department colleagues can not go out of town, I need to be responsible for the installation and training.
We are ready to cooperate, he sent equipment from Wuhan to Jingmen, I rushed from Changsha to install and training.
Changsha to Jingmen nearly 500 km, the normal drive more than four hours, extraordinary times, I have to do some preparation. Now Hubei traffic is closed, I quickly contact the customer for me to open a pass, we this is to serve the task of the epidemic, is released. With this key item in hand, I packed my protective gear, and I put a lot of mineral water in the car for the 3:00 p.m. departure.
I got on the highway with my GPS, and as I walked, the GPS told me to get off the highway. Later I thought it might be because of the road closure and the navigation was not clear how to go.
As soon as I got off the highway, I knew I was in trouble. I had to get back on the highway to get to Jingmen. Took a section of national highway, probably in Qianjiang, Hubei Province. At an intersection, the front road closure, I saw other cars turned into a fork, I also followed the turn into.
It was now six or seven o'clock in the evening, and it was getting dark, and I was driving into a village. I tried to drive out, but there were mounds of dirt at many junctions, some of which were blocked by a tractor. I've been driving around this village, and I can't find my way out.
A roadblock on a country road
I had no choice. I got out of the car and knocked on the door of a house. The villager gave me the party secretary's telephone number. I went to the village party secretary and told him that I was there to deliver the equipment, to help with the new pneumonia test. Village Party secretary a listen to, attach importance to, immediately call someone to move the tractor, let me out.

With the help of the Party secretary, I finally left the village.
A roadblock on a country road
But the frustration isn't over yet. After walking for a while, I was blocked by a bigger mound. I got out of the car to look for a plank and tried to bridge it, but the mound was too high and did not succeed. A colleague called and asked where I was? I'm in a hurry, too.

Then a guy came by, and I asked him how he was gonNA get out. He said he knew an exit, and he drove me on his motorcycle to a place where I could get to the highway. So late, it is the new year, I am particularly grateful to this fellow, out of money to give him a red envelope, but the fellow did not want.
After two hours of driving around the country, I finally got back on the highway.
Arriving in Jingmen late at night
With a pass, I was able to get into Jingmen, and it was 11:00 at night. I called my teachers at the CDC, and they were busy with other tasks, and they told me to set up the machine the next day. These days they are working overtime, especially hard.

Jingmen has entered a state of emergency, no hotel normal business, fortunately, the CDC teachers to help me contact their recent overtime rest hotel, give me a room to stay. To the hotel, I made a bowl of instant noodles to eat, this time found very hungry Ah.
Before going to bed, I gave the CDC the next day to do training program, coronavirus extraction analysis and judgment, and the World Health Organization (WHO) guidelines information, and so on, carried out a number of combing and rewinding, hope to help the CDC teachers as soon as possible familiar with equipment and optimization of experimental programs.
Peng Xin
The next morning to the CDC to install machines, to do training for technical staff. We usually work with special overalls, to do some protection, but wearing such a high-grade protective clothing work is the first time. Because of the new crown disease, the CDC has also raised the standard of protection.

Busy until 1:00 pm, all the work completed, the disease control teacher ordered takeout, we all ate a hot meal.
At the Jingmen Center for Disease Control and Prevention
Lunch box, I have to hurry back to Changsha, the road is another 6 hours, relying on Red Bull "life" .

Set off for Hunan
I've been working at Roche Diagnostics for five years, and I've done some urgent work before. For example, African swine fever, which is quite serious, we provide detection equipment to the animal epidemic prevention department, which plays an important role in the control of the epidemic. But there is no human-to-human transmission of swine fever, which most people may not realize, but in the animal husbandry industry, it is a very serious epidemic.

Next, we may go to Hubei several times. Now is the time when we need high-quality nucleic acid detection instruments. We can make some contribution to fight the epidemic by doing this work. I feel quite happy.
Come and go, tossing and turning, all the way to meet too many good people, let me moved, I also want to do more responsibility. There are more than ten million medical staff on the front lines, and we will do everything we can to support you. Hubei brothers and sisters, we have been with you! Come on!
